who am i? 

i am a faculty member in the department
of computer science , johns hopkins university. i am also a member
of the center for language and
speech processing here at hopkins. my research interests include natural
language processing, spoken language systems, machine learning and artificial
intelligence. my e-mail address is brill@cs.jhu.edu i look nothing like that picture. not yet, at least. 







